# .dockerignore — giảm context build, tránh leak local artifacts.

**/bin/
**/obj/
**/out/
**/publish/
**/TestResults/
**/coverage/
**/.vs/
**/.vscode/
**/.idea/
**/.git/
**/.github/
**/.claude/
**/node_modules/
**/Thumbs.db
**/.DS_Store

# Secret files — KHÔNG bao giờ vào image
**/appsettings.Development.json
**/appsettings.Local.json
**/secrets.json
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/*.pfx
**/*.key
**/*.pem

# Doc / IaC không cần trong image runtime
docs/
infra/
tests/fixtures/
Dockerfile
.dockerignore
